The '''Coruscant Accords''' were the collections of guidelines that determined what a [[Planet/Legends|planet]] needed to do to join, and remain, a member of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]]. They were presumably established during the [[Unification Wars (Galactic Republic)|Unification Wars]] as part of the [[Galactic Constitution/Legends|Galactic Constitution]].

